# TechCrush WebApp

This is a simple web application project for TechCrush tutorials.

## Getting Started

To view the web app:

- Open `index.html` in your web browser for the entry point.
- Click on "Go to Homepage" to access the main homepage at `homepage.html`.

## Project Structure

- `index.html`: Entry point with link to homepage
- `homepage.html`: Main homepage with navigation and sections
- `styles.css`: Stylesheet for the web pages
- `README`: This file

## Features

- Responsive design
- Navigation menu
- Sections for About, Features, and Contact
- Clean and modern styling

## Contributing

Feel free to contribute by adding more features, pages, or improving the design.
